# Changes Made to Complete the Admin Dashboard

## Summary
Built the complete backend admin module to support the existing frontend admin dashboard.
The frontend (`admin-dashboard.js`, `admin-login.html`) was already making API calls to `/admin/*`
endpoints that did not exist in the backend. All those endpoints are now implemented.

---

## New Files

### Backend — Admin Module (`BE/src/modules/admin/`)

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `admin.controller.ts` | Express router with 7 routes for admin |
| `admin.service.ts` | Handles product update, original price tracking, and offer creation/deletion logic |
| `admin.middleware.ts` | JWT Bearer token verification |
| `offer.helpers.ts` | **(NEW)** Shared functions to calculate discounts, apply/revert offers to products |
| `offer.cron.ts` | **(NEW)** Cron job that runs every 60s to detect and expire offers |

### Backend — Offer System Overhaul

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `product.schema.ts` | Added `originalPrice` field |
| `interfaces/index.ts` | Added `originalPrice` to `IProduct` |
| `product.dto.ts` | Added `originalPrice` |
| `entity/index.ts` | Added `originalPrice` to `Product` |
| `factory/index.ts` | Initialization sets `originalPrice = price` |
| `product.service.ts` | Auto-detects active offers when creating a new product and applies discount |
| `index.ts` | Added `scheduleOfferExpiry()` to run background cron job |

