## Offer Auto-Apply System Tests Performed
- ✅ Create offer: automatically discounts all existing products in the matching category
- ✅ Add product: adding a new product to a category with an active offer auto-applies the discount
- ✅ Delete offer: deleting an offer automatically reverts all affected products to `originalPrice`
- ✅ Expire offer: background cron job detects expiry, sets `isActive=false`, and reverts products
- ✅ Edit pricing: updating the price from the admin UI explicitly updates the `originalPrice`, allowing the discount to intelligently recalculate


